67
00:05:32,491 --> 00:05:33,492
aku akan turun tangan.

68
00:05:34,827 --> 00:05:36,037
Aku akan membunuhnya.

69
00:05:36,579 --> 00:05:37,997
Jadi, semangatlah, Jiyong.

70
00:05:38,998 --> 00:05:39,832
Kau punya aku.

71
