-Hormat!
-Hormat!

310
00:23:54,802 --> 00:23:56,262
Hormat!

311
00:23:57,763 --> 00:23:58,764
Hormat.

312
00:24:00,808 --> 00:24:01,809
Istirahat di tempat.

313
